{"tid":606732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴利不排除未來去中國發展","createTime":"2018-03-26T16:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T01:30:36.000Z","uid":166054,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0504e47acff34edb014b6addd1cc41cfab091f8c","tid":606732,"uid":166054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"加里夫巴利現時仍然是皇家馬德里球員，不過他說未來有日可能會轉去中超聯賽發展。<br />\n<br />\n威爾斯代表隊成員巴利正在參加中國盃比賽，不過他的職業生涯未來仍然是個問號，因為這位28歲球星今季在皇馬失勢，因為受傷減少上陣機會。<br />\n<br />\n然而，巴利仍然很受各大豪門歡迎，即使他下季不留在皇馬，仍然不愁出路。<br />\n<br />\n巴利說參加中國盃的感覺不錯，未來有可能來中國發展：<span style=\"color: red;\">「中國是偉大的國家，有良好的人民。</span>不過未來如何，我看不到那麼遠，老實地講。但只能講，如果我來中國，一定會好好地受到照顧。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://goal.com/article/uuid/43522672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com%2Farticle%2Fuuid%2F43522672&d=fH3zLyykv1JNjY51DHDM8DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f2c4df5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goal.com/article/uuid/43522672</a>"},{"pid":"4108ed9bc8d4f6109878c3675416d51bfa1a157e","tid":606732,"uid":77805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T19:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936a4af6841bdb512073c93af07979d65bfd4163","tid":606732,"uid":166054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4108ed9bc8d4f6109878c3675416d51bfa1a157e","tid":606732,"uid":77805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T19:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T19:27:08.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲嘢都噏得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423476718beacb3bde01cb855d3e18623fc1d6d4","tid":606732,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T19:28:26.000Z","msg":"點睇都係『香港是偉大的國家，有良好的人民』順眼啲"},{"pid":"050b0eff3f7833a902777aac6a312007f6828042","tid":606732,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"英格蘭是偉大的國家，有良好的人民"},{"pid":"aa782456b2e60e30a171adb30f1e0be1b9ca40f6","tid":606732,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:44:29.000Z","msg":"人良唔良好我唔知<br />\n但d球員一定想買起佢對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffa6f0298774f63b8102ffd9be31c3c72ea3fc9","tid":606732,"uid":79391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"成37歲啦 去掘金啦"},{"pid":"9d6860dd936d849841408e597aa722e180b7cc14","tid":606732,"uid":10671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:22:02.000Z","msg":"佢呢D玻璃腳去支那踢兩場會唔會就比人踢到斷腳收山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcc1b4da616215cce6f5b9247db5c80f34acccf","tid":606732,"uid":70800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"畀人hi 一hi又可以養傷 傷到完約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a88002299c4f71357a7b1d0bb604ce34d53f01c","tid":606732,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6860dd936d849841408e597aa722e180b7cc14","tid":606732,"uid":10671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:22:02.000Z","msg":"佢呢D玻璃腳去支那踢兩場會唔會就比人踢到斷腳收山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"加坦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f700ae20b764365b0a5f933d65a919605e9c7690","tid":606732,"uid":59966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6860dd936d849841408e597aa722e180b7cc14","tid":606732,"uid":10671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:22:02.000Z","msg":"佢呢D玻璃腳去支那踢兩場會唔會就比人踢到斷腳收山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:27:16.000Z","msg":"要學tevez咁